videos.description: Kihei Clark throws a wild lob from the top of the key and Jay Huff manages to get up high enough to tip it in.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Virginia's Huff tips in difficult lob off his fingertips) 2019/11/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Virginia's Huff tips in difficult lob off his fingertips

videos.description: Marek Dolezaj gets the ball in the post and throws a no-look pass out to Buddy Boeheim who knocks down a Syracuse 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Syracuse's Dolezaj throws nice no-look pass to Boeheim for 3) 2019/11/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Syracuse's Dolezaj throws nice no-look pass to Boeheim for 3

videos.description: After having his shot blocked by Casey Morsell, Elijah Hughes steals the ball back and squeezes through defenders to make a difficult and-1 layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hughes recovers blocked shot and makes difficult and-1 finger roll) 2019/11/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hughes recovers blocked shot and makes difficult and-1 finger roll
